WOTE 1380 AM, 96.5 FM AND 94.9 FM
BRAND: THE FRANCHISE SPORTS RADIO
The Franchise is focused on discussing sports news, analysis, and commentary. It includes live coverage of sports events, interviews with athletes and coaches, and debates among sports commentators. This format is popular among sports fans who want to keep up with the latest sports news and analysis. The Franchise features a great mix of Wisconsin Sports Talk mixed with National Shows from Fox Sports Radio.
Feature Programming: High School Sports, Wisconsin Badger Football, NFL Playoffs, NCAA Final Four, Local News and Sports
Over the Air Coverage: Shawano, Waupaca, and Menominee Counties.
Stream: WOTERADIO.COM
